com.sap.spe.condmgnt.finding

Interface ICondition

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IFreeGoodsCondition, IGroupConditionUserExit, IHeaderCondition, IPricingCondition, IPricingConditionCommon, IPricingConditionSAPExit, IPricingConditionUserExit

    public interface ICondition
    Interface for the condition-object. For pricing this object corresponds to an A***-record in R/3.
